2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses a channel model for 5G air interface designs, which are related to networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with millimeter-wave communications, which are used for high-speed multimedia applications. 
4. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking): The paper presents a channel model for outdoor communications, which falls under the category of communications and networking. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses a modeling procedure for generating channel coefficients, which involves system modeling and control.
